全国21省份22日零新增，抗疫战果继续巩固。
Twenty-two provinces in the country added 22 new, the battle against the disease continued to consolidate.
此前我们预测湖北疑似病例存量，在拉网排查取得成功后会于22日开始下降，最新数据确实印证了该预测文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进 图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|谢丽容一、累计确诊病例：全国新冠肺炎病例总数有望控制在8万截至2月22日24:00，全国累计报告确诊新冠肺炎病例76936例。
The latest figures do confirm the latest figures. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
以下为分区趋势图。
The following is the zoning trend chart.
图1.1红线和黑线显示我们在和“死神”赛跑！图1.2武汉以外地区的趋势线平顶已经清晰，目前大体可以看出：国内非湖北地区累计病例将停留在13000例左右，湖北非武汉地区将在19000例左右，武汉将在48000例左右。
Fig. 1.1 The red and black lines show that we are in a race with death! Figure 1.2 The trend line outside Wuhan is clear, and it can be seen that the total number of cases in non-Hubei areas will stay around 13,000, in Hubei non-Wuhan region around 19,000, Wuhan will be about 48,000.
最主要的变数是，这个新冠肺炎究竟是像SARS一样不留长尾，还是会如指数函数所示的拖出一条长长的尾巴（最近有专家有此担心）？亦或介于两者之间？要待非湖北地区数据先行确认。
The main variable is whether the new crown pneumonia has a long tail, like SARS, or a long tail, as suggested by the exponential function (some experts have recently worried), or somewhere in between? Until non-Hubei data are confirmed.
二、新增病例：北京迎来零新增！非湖北地区全面收官图2国内非湖北地区新增病例进一步降至18例，平均每省市0.6例。
New cases: zero new cases in Beijing: zero new cases in non-Hubei area.Figure 2 The number of new cases in non-Hubei areas of China further decreased to 18, with an average of 0.6 cases per province.
零新增省市21个，北京迎来了疫情爆发后的首个“零新增”。
No new provinces and cities 21, Beijing ushered in the outbreak of the first "zero new."
图3今日湖北统计口径调整，在原18市州外新列监狱一项。
Fig. 3 Hubei statistical adjustment today, in the original 18 outside the state of the new prison.
这个数据是扩大统计范围还是将原有统计数据重新归类尚未明确，其对数据趋势影响有待观察。
It is not clear whether the data will be extended or regrouped, and its impact on data trends remains to be seen.
我们推测是因为进一步强化防疫属地管理原则而刚刚被纳入统计。
We speculate that further strengthening of the principles of territorial management of epidemic prevention has just been incorporated into the statistics.
但无论如何数据公布本身都是特别值得称赞的！疫情当头，群众更希望看到一个坚定自信的政府。
But in any case, the data release itself is particularly praiseworthy! With the epidemic at hand, the public would prefer to see a strong and confident government.
从昨天情况看监狱的新增病例数紧随武汉，超过湖北其他市州。
Judging from yesterday's situation, the number of new cases followed Wuhan, ahead of other Hubei cities.
疫情在监狱爆发是个不幸，相信局面正得到控制。
The outbreak in prison was unfortunate and it is believed that the situation is being brought under control.
总体不改变对湖北向好趋势判断。
Overall did not change Hubei to good trend judgment.
图4武汉的新增病例有所回升。
Fig. 4 New cases recovered in Wuhan.
结合湖北新增疑似、疑似排除和疑似隔离等数据，分析认为这主要是受拉网筛查和加快检测速度推进“日结清零”等措施影响而非疫情反弹。
Combined with the new suspected, suspected and suspected isolation data in Hubei Province, the analysis suggests that this is mainly due to the impact of measures such as screening and accelerated detection speed to "daily clearance zero" rather than a rebound of the epidemic.
不改变对武汉战局已发生积极逆转的判断。
Does not change the Wuhan war situation has taken a positive reversal of the judgment.
三、确诊病例增长率：非湖北地区增速“趋零”，湖北及武汉略回升，但不改趋势判断图5国内非湖北地区增长率降至0.18%，统计意义上已经“趋零”。
The rate of increase of confirmed cases is zero in non-Hubei areas, Hubei and Wuhan have recovered slightly, but without changing the trend, the growth rate of non-Hubei areas has been reduced to 0.18%, which is statistically zero.
湖北及武汉略有回升，有拉网排查检测加快推进“日结清零”因素，但也不排除·数据调整因素。
Hubei and Wuhan pick up a little, there are pull net inspection to speed up the "day-to-day clearance of zero" factor, but also do not exclude data adjustment factors.
均不改变原向好趋势判断。
Do not change the original trend of good judgment.
四、密切接触者追踪：湖北及武汉的追踪力度强势提升图6湖北这个指标继续爬升！近三日的滑动平均数更显示其升势强劲：追踪比已进一步提高到20左右。
Close Contacts Tracing: Hubei and Wuhan Tracking Strength Rising Figure 6 Hubei This indicator continues to climb! The three-day average shows a strong rise: the tracking ratio has further increased to around 20.
据报2月21日晚湖北省委书记应勇针对武汉主战场部署工作时明确指出“要进一步加强流调，强化流调队伍建设和大数据分析，完善（流调-隔离-筛查-治疗-流调的）工作闭环”，“在具备条件情况下，实现武汉市全部密切接触人员集中隔离”。
On the night of Feb. 21, when responding to the deployment of Wuhan Main Battlefield, the secretary of Hubei Provincial Party Committee Yingyong clearly stated that "we need to further strengthen the flow pattern, strengthen the construction of the transfer team and big data analysis, improve the (transfer-isolation-screening-treatment-transfer) closed-loop."
此举将彻底阻隔传染，令人鼓舞。
It is encouraging that this will completely prevent infection.
图7湖北和非湖北地区都在继续下降，意味着可以释放更多医疗资源、社会人力资源和隔离空间投入到新的密切接触者追踪隔离上。
Fig. 7 Both Hubei and non-Hubei regions continue to decline, meaning that more medical resources, social human resources, and isolated spaces can be released to new close contacts.
五、疑似病例：增量下降，湖北存量继拉网筛查行动后也再现下降图8湖北（含武汉）新增疑似病例继续向下，确认武汉“五个百分之百”功成。
Suspected cases: Incremental decline, Hubei stock following the screening operation also reproduce the decline Figure 8 Hubei (including Wuhan) new suspected cases continue to downward, confirmed Wuhan "five hundred percent" success.
图9此前我们预测湖北在拉网排查取得成功后会于今日开始下降，今日果然如此！印证“拉网筛查”战果。
Fig. 9 We predicted that Hubei will start to decline today after the success of trawling. This is true today.
六、在院治疗人数：湖北非湖北都在下降。
The number of people in hospital treatment: Hubei non-Hubei are falling.
“湖北确诊未入院”人数亦有下降图10在院治疗人数存量下降，继续释放病床床位。
Figure 10 The number of people in hospital treatment fell, continue to release beds.
我们推测出的“湖北确诊未入院”人数亦有下降。
We speculate that the number of people diagnosed as unhospitalized in Hubei province has also decreased.
七、病死率、治愈率图11病死率已连续提高两周以上，估计还会持续。
fatality rate and cure rate Figure 11 The fatality rate has been rising for more than two weeks and is expected to continue.
这里有病死发生时间与新确诊增加不同步的因素（非湖北地区），也有救治能力和医疗资源因素（武汉）。
There are the factors that increase the time of disease death and new diagnosis (non-Hubei area), but also the ability of treatment and medical resources (Wuhan).
图12治愈率以更快速度上升。
Fig. 12 The cure rate is increasing at a faster rate.
让我们和死神赛跑！八、新增出院和新增确诊图13.1新出院人数与新确诊人数图13.2核心医疗资源继续得到释放。
New discharges and new diagnoses Figure 13.1 New discharges and newly diagnosed figures 13.2 Core medical resources continue to be released.
小结：湖北及武汉向好趋势不改。
Summary: Hubei and Wuhan to the good trend unchanged.
全国非湖北地区疫情蔓延已得到遏制。
The spread of the epidemic in non-Hubei areas has been curbed.
新增病例统计意义上已“趋零”。
The number of new cases is statistically zero.
统计上未见疫情卷土重来证据，也未发现意味着疫情死灰复燃的个案。
There was no statistically significant evidence of a resurgence of the epidemic, nor was there any evidence of a resurgence of the disease.
继续呼吁湖北以外地区在防控意识不松懈的前提下，加快有序复工复产。
Continue to call on areas outside Hubei in the prevention and control awareness of the premise of speeding up orderly resumption of production.
